4815-tools-build-actions.title: Build Actions
4815-tools-build-actions.contents1:
Build the project and automatically download the program when a VEX product is connected.
Only recompile the changed source files.
[Start Flow (Build)](command:4815-tools.flow-build)
Recompile all source files. Try this if "Build" doesn't work.
[Start Flow (Rebuild)](command:4815-tools.flow-rebuild)
4815-tools-build-actions.contents2: This is not a VEXcode project. Please open a VEXcode project to use build actions.
Create a commit and push to the remote server
[Backup Changes](command:4815-tools.backup-changes)
Pull commits from the remote server.
[Pull Changes](command:4815-tools.pull-changes)
4815-tools-project-management.title: Project Management
4815-tools-project-management.contents:
Open a 4815 project from the project home directory.
[Open Project](command:4815-tools.open-project)
Clone a project from the remote server.
[Clone Project](command:4815-tools.clone-project)
Create a new project from a template and push to the remote server. (optional)
[Create Project](command:4815-tools.create-project)
Link the local project to the remote server and create one if needed.
[Setup Project & Remote](command:4815-tools.setup-project-and-remote)
